                <h1>Effective Physical Therapy for Pain Relief & Mobility</h1>
                <p>A physical therapist helps individuals improve their mobility and manage pain through personalized treatment plans, exercises, and rehabilitative techniques. They play a vital role in recovery from injuries, surgeries, and chronic conditions. Their goal is to enhance physical function and quality of life for patients of all ages.</p>
